      <paragraph>Authentication resources enable you authenticate users via <external-ref href="https://developers.facebook.com/docs/facebook-login/"/> or <external-ref href="http://www.mozilla.org/en-US/persona/"/>.</paragraph>
      <paragraph>The following table lists the authentication resources.</paragraph>
      <table>
         <header>
            <row>
               <entry>HTTP Method</entry>
